322
00:15:12,919 --> 00:15:15,080
(Yutian's
current top management is rigid.)

323
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:19,679
(The development of Yutian
is also stagnant.)

324
00:15:21,479 --> 00:15:23,239
(But we are confident that,)

325
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:27,200
