397
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:16,839
I'm telling you that,

398
00:19:17,239 --> 00:19:17,599
one day...

399
00:19:17,599 --> 00:19:19,160
although he seems like

400
00:19:19,239 --> 00:19:20,880
