477
00:23:32,520 --> 00:23:33,479
Ok?

478
00:23:35,119 --> 00:23:38,119
Xiangyuan, you just do it for me.

479
00:23:38,479 --> 00:23:39,400
Ok?

480
00:23:42,839 --> 00:23:43,719
Fanlv,

481
00:23:44,520 --> 00:23:45,479
