507
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:56,000
can be used as a legal evidence?

508
00:24:57,439 --> 00:24:58,400
No.

509
00:24:58,560 --> 00:24:59,400
So,

510
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,800
