551
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:33,880
No.

552
00:26:34,839 --> 00:26:36,119
Lei Yuzheng should be very busy.

553
00:26:36,239 --> 00:26:37,520
He should not want anyone to bother him.

554
00:26:37,959 --> 00:26:39,880
